25 NEW SECTION. Section 6. Transition -- rights of personnel -- rights to property -- rules and
26 orders -- legal proceedings -- rights of duties under existing transactions -- references. (1) (a) The
27 workers' compensation judge and each employee of the office of workers' compensation judge affected by the
28 transfer of the office from the executive branch to the judicial branch are entitled to all rights that the judge or
