6 NEW SECTION. Section 7. Retirement plan election for workers' compensation judge. A
7 workers' compensation judge who is an active member of the public employees' retirement system on [the
8 effective date of this act] may elect to remain under that system by notifying the public employees' retirement
9 board in writing of the election on or before October 1, 2025.
